редложением и призывом к действию. Подходит для продвижения одной услуги, акции или продукта."}],["$","ul","4",{"className":"space-y-2 my-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Фрилансер: 15 000–40 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","1",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Небольшая студия: 40 000–100 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","2",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Крупная студия: от 100 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","3",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Типичный срок: 5–14 дней"}]]}]]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Адекватная цена за качественный лендинг с SEO-оптимизацией, мобильной версией и формой заявки — 30 000–60 000 рублей у опытного фрилансера или небольшой команды."}],["$","h3","6",{"className":"font-display text-xl text-light uppercase leading-tight mt-6 mb-3","children":"Корпоративный сайт (5–15 страниц)"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Сайт компании с разделами «Услуги», «О нас», «Кейсы», «Контакты». Оптимален для малого бизнеса, который хочет присутствие в интернете и органический трафик."}],["$","ul","8",{"className":"space-y-2 my-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Фрилансер: 40 000–80 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","1",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Небольшая студия: 80 000–200 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","2",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Крупная студия: от 200 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","3",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Типичный срок: 10–21 день"}]]}]]}],["$","h3","9",{"className":"font-display text-xl text-light uppercase leading-tight mt-6 mb-3","children":"Интернет-магазин"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Каталог с корзиной, оплатой и личным кабинетом. Самый трудоёмкий тип: требует интеграции с платёжными системами, логистикой и CRM."}],["$","ul","11",{"className":"space-y-2 my-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Небольшой магазин (до 500 товаров): 80 000–150 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","1",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Средний магазин: 150 000–400 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","2",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-accent mt-1 flex-shrink-0","children":"—"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Крупный e-commerce: от 400 000 ₽"}]]}],["$","li","3",{"className":"font-body text-light/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"clas